Pick up the coffee cup from the coffee machine.

Put the coffee cup in the refrigerator and take the coffee cup out of the refrigerator.

Put the coffee cup in the coffee machine.

Place the mug at the coffee maker.

Pick up the mug from the coffee maker
Move to the fridge to the right of the sink
Chill the mug in the fridge for a moment
Move to the coffee maker to the left of the sink
Put the mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: walk to the left a little
grab the cup from the coffee machine
turn around, walk to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, put the cup in, wait a while, take the cup out
turn around, walk to the coffee machine
put the cup on the coffee machine

grab the coffee cup out from the spout of the coffee maker
turn around and walk over to the fridge on the left side of the room
place the cup inside of the fridge and let it cool down, then take it back out
turn left and walk to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter on the left side of the room
place the coffee cup under the spout of the coffee maker

high_descs: Move to the left and face the coffee maker.
Pick the black mug up from under the coffee maker.
Go right and then right again before turning left to face the fridge.
Put the cup in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the cup out and shut the door.
Go left and then left again before turning right to face the coffee maker.
